Package: heckeengine
Title: QOU Hecke-engine Gram + Markov-trace Primitives
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Quantum Observable Universe contributors",
                     role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "noreply@anthropic.com"))
Description: R bindings to the QOU `hecke-engine` Rust crate via
    extendr. Exposes the Iwahori-Hecke H_3(q) Gram matrix, Markov-trace
    weights, and substrate-q convenience functions. Mirrors the
    cross-language surface of `pyhecke-native` (Python), `@litlfred/hecke-engine-node`
    (Node.js), `@litlfred/hecke-engine-wasm` (browser), and `hecke-engine-jvm`
    (Kotlin/Swift via UniFFI).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc, libgmp-dev, libmpfr-dev
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.0
URL: https://github.com/litlfred/qou
BugReports: https://github.com/litlfred/qou/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
